value: たあっ
そこだ！
くっ…
いかんな…
Made your peace, have you?
Do not make haste for death.
I'll finish this with a single blow!
Allow me to demonstrate.
I, too, must surrender to death?
Sigh...
Quite a change, wouldn't you say? In any attire, I am still Eldigan.
Behave yourself! Should you not be above such childish tricks?
You believe me to look good in this? Consider me...flattered...
My friends, my family, my country... My hope is that they prosper.
This outfit makes an apt pairing with the Demon Sword Mystletainn I wield, does it not?
What I desire is an honorable death—one befitting a knight.
Under my protection, your death shall be kept at bay.
Understood.
Hm...
Let them meet their end.
